                            <a href="#" class="btn text-white">Book Now</a>
                        </div>                       
                    </div>
                    <div class="slider-card">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-4">
                            <img class="offers-img" src="~/Assets/img/health.png" alt=" ">
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0 text-center"><b>Health Insurance</b></h5>
                        <p class="text-center p-1">Access wide range of hospitals and get the best treatment without worrying about bills. Compare affordable and custome health insurance plan for you.</p>
                        <div class="button text-center p-2">
                            <a href="#" class="btn text-white">Book Now</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="slider-card">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-4">
                            <img class="offers-img" src="~/Assets/img/home.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0 text-center"><b>Home Insurance</b></h5>
                        <p class="text-center p-1">Home insurance provides coverage for your home and personal belongings whether you own a home or live as a tenant.</p>
                        <div class="button text-center p-2">
                            <a href="#" class="btn text-white">Book Now</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="slider-card">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center mb-4">
                            <img class="offers-img" src="~/Assets/img/car.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <h5 class="mb-0 text-center"><b>Car Insurance</b></h5>
                        <p class="text-center p-1">Car insurance is the best care anyone can give to his car. Compare the widest coverage and affordable plans to take informed decisions</p>
                        <div class="button text-center p-2">
                            <a href="#" class="btn text-white">Book Now</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
